snippet.title: Naive Boy Super Lash | Announce Trailer | PS4, PS5 & Steam
snippet.description:
Naive Boy Super Lash, the game that tries to be a whip simulator is coming soon on PS4, PS5 and Steam. Wishlist now!

PS Store:  https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10008452
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3040400/Naive_Boy_Super_Lash/
